---
title: Double Seared Steak & Mumbai Coconut Sauce  with Herby Potatoes & Cucumber Salad
description: We can't work out which is best: the golden roasted potatoes, the gentle warmth of the creamy Mumbai-spiced coconut sauce or the crunch of the cucumber salad. Go on, you decide!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
